name: Android-tracker
body:
This project is basically to track your day by day activities on your android device automatically and to send a mail in the pre-selected time to your email account.

TO check further description in detail check the following link:

https://www.dropbox.com/s/1b0qjgt1f3javqp/Code%20%285%29.pdf?dl=0

Thanks
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
